# StreamScopeChart - Realtime Graph Generator

StreamScopeChart renders clean, real-time line graphs for monitoring sensor input, simulations, or metrics.

## Features
- Live updates  
- Scrollable chart  
- Matplotlib-based  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_StreamScopeChart.git
cd 25_StreamScopeChart
python visualize.py
